a.n: World Grand Prix Fight TNA, 1/8th finals, TATNEFT CUP, Tatneft Arena, Kazan, Russia

p.d: The fourth stage of the 1/8th finals of the "TATNEFT CUP" tournament, which took place in Kazan (Russia), at the "Tatneft Arena" in Ice Sports Palace. Six events are scheduled for the event in three weight categories involving fighters from Russia, France, Uzbekistan, Georgia, Greece and Armenia.
